{"name":"Erz Agrious","size":"medium","type":"fey","tag":"Legendary Bear Faerie","alignment":"","hitDice":"16","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":4,"otherArmorDesc":"19 (+upcast) (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"20","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"20","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"60 (+10 per upcast)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"21","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"18","intPoints":"11","wisPoints":"15","chaPoints":"14","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"11","customCr":"12 (8,400 XP)","customProf":4,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"[MON] can take 1 legendary action, choosing from the options below, which it can take only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the archmage can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the archmage can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The archmage can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the archmage's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the archmage's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the archmage dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Magic Resistance","desc":"The [MON] has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes one bite attack, one claw attack, and can use its Gnarlbound Bellow (if available)."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 4D6] piercing damage and the target is grappled."},{"name":"Claw","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack_: [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: [STR 2d6] (+upcast) slashing damage."},{"name":"Gnarlbound Bellow (Recharge 6)","desc":"[MON] roars and pulls a pulse destructive energy pulses inward from a 30-foot sphere. Each other creature in that area must make a DC [STR SAVE] Strength saving throw . On a failed save, a creature takes [3d6] thunder damage and is pulled 15ft towards [MON]. A creature who succeeds takes half as much damage and is not pulled."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Turn One: Charge","desc":"[MON] moves his speed and takes one claw attack. The target must succeed on a DC [STR SAVE] strength saving throw or be knocked prone."},{"name":"Turn Two: Charge Up","desc":"[MON] takes the dodge action and automatically recharges his Gnarlbound Bellow."},{"name":"Turn Three: Etherealness","desc":"[MON] and any creatures it's grappling vanish into the ethereal plane. Spells which target a creature aphysically can penetrate through to creatures taken to the ethereal plane in this way. As an action, [MON] may reenter the material plane, at which point the grappled creature does as well."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"lightning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"slashing","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"thunder","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":false},{"name":"Common","speaks":false},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":false},{"name":"Elvish","speaks":false},{"name":"Sylvan","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Erz","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}